divs: Sighting DetailsMe and a buddy of mine were on the patio over by coronado highschool, when i noticed a star-like object from my pov the object was moving N to S slow and was not blinking like the strobes on a plane thats why i curious what could it be it seem to be east of the city but im only guessing. only saw it very shortly before it moved behind a tree line.
